msgid "Jeremy opened by noting that DDD seems to be experiencing renewed interest, with multiple presentation requests recently. He theorizes this resurgence relates to the rise of AI-assisted development and agentic systems, where DDD's structured approach to organizing business logic makes it easier for AI tools to understand and generate code."
msgstr ""

